    "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nRight now for TopN we first fully sort an input batch, then we slice it. This is dumb because we have to move around the data way too much.\r\n\r\nWe should get the sort order instead. Then take the topN of the sort order, and finally gather just that from the original input.\r\n\r\nEven if N is very large, this is no worse than what we do today.",
